            oneself, distraught</span>, with pain, grief (<i><span class="en">Il. 24.12</span></i>), or sometimes with joy (<i><span class="en">Od. 18.333</span></i>); <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀλύ̄ων</span>, ‘frantic with pain,’ <i><span class="en">Od.
            9.398</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
